<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She's been treating herself to brief breaks from her typically busy schedule as she adjusts to life in the US.</p>

<p>And Dua Lipa appeared in great spirits as she packed on the PDA with her boyfriend Anwar Hadid during an al fresco dinner date in New York City on Wednesday evening.</p>

<p>The singer, 25, stood out in a bright graphic T-shirt and a powder blue jumper as she enjoyed the company of her model beau, 21. </p>

<p>Loved-up: Dua Lipa appeared in great spirits as she packed on the PDA with her boyfriend Anwar Hadid during an al fresco dinner date in New York City on Wednesday evening</p>

<p>The loved-up couple kissed and cuddled as they caught up over some street food, before they puffed on cigarettes outside the eatery.</p>

<p>Cutting a stylish figure, the Break My Heart hitmaker teamed her colourful look with wide-leg denim jeans and chunky black trainers.</p>

<p>The musician added a touch of girly glamour to her edgy appearance as she carried her essentials in a leather handbag, and accessorised with gold jewellery.</p>

<p>Her raven locks were worn in a straight style, while she nailed vampy chic in the beauty department with winged eyeliner and dewy foundation. </p>

<p>LA native Anwar, who was seen carrying their new rescue pooch Dexter, opted for an all-black outfit during his romantic evening. </p>

